features: 🗂️File Folder - The package contains 120 pcs colored folders with 120 white lables, a total of 6 colors (Blue, Green, Yellow, Orange, Red, Purple), bright colors to enrich your office life
🏷️1/3 Cut Tab - Each file folder features a 1/3 cut tab, allowing for easy labeling and quick identification of contents. Pencil or erasable pen can be used to write marks

📄Expandable Capacity - There are three expansion sublines at the bottom that can hold up to 120 sheets of paper. Designed to accommodate letter-sized documents, these file folders are perfect for organizing your important papers, reports, invoices, or school assignments
👍Premium Quality - Made from durable and heavyweight paper stock, these file folders are built to withstand daily use and keep your documents safe and secure

✅Stay Organized - Whether you're organizing work-related documents, school assignments, or personal files, these colored file folders are up to the task. Say goodbye to cluttered desks and hello to a more efficient workspace

Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Basic Colorful Folders
reviews.reviewText: I got this 120 pack of colorful paper file folders for my home office. They are great basic file folders - sturdy and well-made, not flimsy, and the colors are nice and bright. My previous set of file folders was plastic, which was nice in one way because they definitely held up to multiple uses, but they were also slick and made it difficult to move papers around, carry them in a stack, etc. I think these sturdy paper folders will hold up well, and they should last me quite a while! Great value for the cost.
